等」。該名醫護指，極度希望病人明白：「呢到係醫院，唔係你屋企，有得比你用唔係本身你應有架」。他指，提供wifi的原因，是因為有些輸入個案，完全無香港網絡，無辦法找到家人，所以提供給他們，強調醫院有規有矩。<br />\n<br />\n醫護續指，有些病人的家人會拿食物到醫院，病人不時要求護士立即拿入去病房，見太耐無人領入病房，居然會自己開病房門出來拿東西，令醫護相當憤怒。該名醫護稱，在家人取餐來醫院前，醫護已講明不會食物一到醫院就立即拿過來，並曾勸病人避免熱食，惟有病人「完全唔聽」，該名醫護反問：「我明住院好慘，中病毒都好慘，但有無諗過醫護係用生命危險黎幫你哋？係你哋做既所作所為前，可唔可以企係醫護立場到諗下？」<br />\n<img src=\"https://image2.stheadline.com/f/432p0/0x0/100/hd/790731da4b03ee05d1c7aabf43f9c550/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200721/_2020072112173215009.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage2.stheadline.com%2Ff%2F432p0%2F0x0%2F100%2Fhd%2F790731da4b03ee05d1c7aabf43f9c550%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200721%2F_2020072112173215009.jpg&h=b0021150&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「HA Secrets」FB截圖<br />\n<a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1824859/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E6%8C%87%E7%97%85%E4%BA%BA%E9%9A%94%E9%9B%A2%E7%97%85%E6%88%BF%E7%95%B6%E9%85%92%E5%BA%97%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E5%A4%9A-Dirty-Team%E9%86%AB%E8%AD%B7%E5%90%90%E5%BF%83%E9%85%B8-%E5%AB%8C%E9%A4%90%E9%9B%A3%E9%A3%9F%E5%8F%88%E6%93%85%E9%96%8B%E6%88%BF%E9%96%80\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1824859%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E6%258C%2587%25E7%2597%2585%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%259A%2594%25E9%259B%25A2%25E7%2597%2585%25E6%2588%25BF%25E7%2595%25B6%25E9%2585%2592%25E5%25BA%2597%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%25B1%2582%25E5%25A4%259A-Dirty-Team%25E9%2586%25AB%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E5%2590%2590%25E5%25BF%2583%25E9%2585%25B8-%25E5%25AB%258C%25E9%25A4%2590%25E9%259B%25A3%25E9%25A3%259F%25E5%258F%2588%25E6%2593%2585%25E9%2596%258B%25E6%2588%25BF%25E9%2596%2580&d=bKbBxrmwQkzC5eAvTqWhP8v4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=9a1e470d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1824859%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E6%258C%2587%25E7%2597%2585%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%259A%2594%25E9%259B%25A2%25